title: Punk Rock Girl
longDescription:
For this product you will receive:

  • Morph Targets
  • Support to live-link
  • Complete control rig for body and face
  • Malleable shaders for the hair and skin
  • IK Foot Placement built-in at the Playable Blueprint
  • Rigged to Unreal Engine Standard model
  • Levels for rendering and overview of the features of the character

DISCLAIMER:

This product supports Lumen for Unreal Engine 5.0+

This product supports Nanite for Unreal Engine 5.0+


Documentation:

https://docs.unrealengine.com/5.0/en-US/lumen-global-illumination-and-reflections-in-unreal-engine/

https://docs.unrealengine.com/5.0/en-US/nanite-virtualized-geometry-in-unreal-engine/


Plugins needed to function properly:


  • LiveLinkControlRig
  • LiveLink
  • LiveLinkCamera
  • AppleARKit
  • AppleARKitFaceSupport
  • HairStrands
